<br>
Second thought came from re-reading feedback,<br>
<br>
Parry: <br>
<br>
Parry is the primary defense of a Mercenary. It would be great to see some sort of other benefit from speccing parry, like the ability to parry arrows, or some other ability. <br>
<br>
Really liking the idea of adding more to skills like parry and block. We're going to be looking at this going forward. Might be a TOA thing (i.e. might be something we address when we're already reworking that area of the code/design for TOA.) <br>
<br>
<br>
I was thinking it would be nice if our off hand got a seperate chance to parry in the evade/parry/block hierarchy.  Currently the game checks to see if an enemy even hit you, then it checks if you evade, then perry, and lastly block.  I would like to see evade, perry mainhand, perry offhand, and lastly block.  Reactionarys should only fire if the mainhand perry's just like dragonfang not fireing when infs evade offhand swings.  This would bring us closer to being true duelwielders and give us a defensive boost since we don't appear to be getting an offensive boost anytime soon.  Best of all assassins don't get perry so it is one way to boost us while not making assassins more overpowered than most think they are now makeing this a tweek we might possible be able to get. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showPrevMessage?topicID=82.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showNextMessage?topicID=82.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=82.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=82.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.threadControl?topicID=82.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=82.topic><img src=http://www.ezbo